QuestData.Title: A Jiro Guide to Not Being Eaten
QuestData.Description:
Devourers attacked. They overran the guardians. They still search for food.
We are not safe. Reduce the devourers' numbers.
This is how not to be eaten.
QuestData.LogDescription: Reduce the devourer presence at the Terrace of Formation.
QuestData.RewardText: Fewer devourers, less likely we will be eaten.
